OL,6,FJersey Airport is no longer under
OL,7,F'special attention' measures.
OL,9,FIt had faced extra oversight from the
OL,10,Faviation regulator since the end of
OL,11,Flast year due to a significant
OL,12,Fmanagement restructuring.
OL,14,FWhistleblowers went on to tell ITV
OL,15,FNews that the changes led to a skills
OL,16,Fgap in safety-critical roles, but
OL,17,FPorts of Jersey says, "After several
OL,18,Fmonths of regular audits, reporting
OL,19,Fand positive engagement, the regulator
OL,20,Fhas confirmed that the additional
OL,21,Foversight is no longer needed".
