OL,4,C'special attention' measures
OL,6,FIt adds that these measures are common
OL,7,F"during periods of significant change
OL,8,Fand, in this instance, to enable the
OL,9,Fnew team to settle into their roles".
OL,11,FJersey Airport Operations Director,
OL,12,FAshley Maggs, adds: "We have a highly
OL,13,Fprofessional team, with a wide variety
OL,14,Fof skills, that works to ensure the
OL,15,Fairport operates smoothly.
OL,17,F"Jersey Airport complies with all
OL,18,Faviation regulations and safe, secure
OL,19,Foperations will always be our most
OL,20,Fimportant priority.
